  • Constructor Details

    • ContactBuilder

      protected ContactBuilder(IType type, int _code)
      The default builder constructor should set the bare minimum properties required to construct a Contact that can be committed to the database. Do not initialize other fields in this constructor unless they really are required and you have checked with all the application teams to make sure the new initialization fits their needs.
